summary: So about Captain Marvel (no spoilers, just some thoughts)
body:
So about Captain Marvel (no spoilers, just some thoughts)

Honestly find it baffling that so many people are so offended by the release of Captain Marvel. I’ve read so many comments about Disney ‘shoving feminism down our throats’ and just general abuse targeted towards not just the movie but also Brie Larson for what? Having the audacity to take on the role of a much loved comic character? Yes, how dare she???? The NERVE. Thing is, I don’t remember Wonder Woman getting this much hate and that’s another female superhero solo movie. I just think it’s strange that just because of a movie being centred around *gasp* a woman even the most devout Marvel fans have decided they can’t even attempt to enjoy a film. Like why can’t you just go into the cinema ready to enjoy another Marvel movie? Why you gotta get so stressed?

title: Gladiator
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2NTjgOj

by rainbowshoes

A Gladiator-style alternate universe:

“Remove your helmet,” Anthony orders.

James hesitates for a moment. He was arrested for Rumlow’s lie that he’d murdered the emperor’s parents. He hadn’t, of course, but that didn’t seem to matter much. Rumlow was close to the Praetor, and he’d said James did it, so James had been arrested. He’d expected to be executed, but then Rumlow had fucking sold him into slavery instead.

He’s only glad he wasn’t executed now, because it gave him the chance to get his revenge.

summary: this is basically my carolmaria timeline!! i also wrote it on this post which is a drawing of their official wedding!! but...
body:
this is basically my carolmaria timeline!! i also wrote it on this post which is a drawing of their official wedding!! but there’s more story in this than the other one

  • ok so
  • carol has found the skrulls a new home and now she’s returning home to earth to stay with maria and monica
  • since the movie was set in the 90s and gays werent allowed in the usaf until 2010 (imma assume that maria is still in the army) and gay marriage wasn’t legalised in usa til 2015
  • they dont get married until 2015
  • but until then
  • ok
  • so
  • maria and carol talk about everything
  • friends, fam, issues, missing each other on that trip that carol just went on
  • but most importantly, maria and monica help carol relearn her past
  • (i mean she has already but like even more)
  • and they were defs in a relationship before this
  • so thats what carol ends up learning from photos and maybe monica if she like slips something out even though her mum told her not to
  • and shes internally like why didn’t maria tell me this
  • but externally shes like oh idk what to do
  • and she starts to slowly fall in love againa
  • and like maria never fell out of love
  • she’s always loved carol no matter what
  • but she didn’t want to push it cause she couldn’t just expect carol to be up for reviving a relationship she barely remembered
  • and there’s a shit ton of pining
  • so much slowburn
  • like maria brushes her hand against carols and shes flustered
  • carol wears more grunge clothing and looks so damn good that marias face is hotter than that kettle carol heated up
  • maria does a stretch in the morning and carol was probably gonna nut
  • vice versa when carol stretchs
  • and eventually monica is like jesus christ and she sets them up
  • like she plans a little picnic date for them outside their house and just watches from the window
  • then from there “auntie carol” becomes “mom”
  • and theyre dating
  • monicas like “fINALLY”
  • and then they spend time together
  • they argue sometimes but never enough to break them apart
  • carol ends up “proposing” to maria a few years later
  • they have a small fake wedding in their field (this part was ripped off another fic i’ll try to find it) and laugh and are cute about it
  • and then gays are allowed in and gay marriage is legalised they get married straight away
  • and it’s rumoured that fury cried at their wedding but no one knows for sure
  • but then the snap happens
  • carol is on a mission (destroying kree or whatever) at the time
  • she begins to watch the people around her turn to dust
  • and she receives the call from fury
  • she realises whats happening and rushes home
  • like she didnt give a fuck what happened
  • she beat up 7 krees grabbed a ship and left
  • she comes home to find the walls covered in dust
  • maria and monica are nowhere to be found
  • she falls on her knees and fucking wails
  • cause now she knows how maria felt
  • she clutches on the things she has left
  • leans on the wall and cries
  • but she knows she can save them so she gets her ass back up
  • she joins the avengers and sets out to fucking murder the dumb bitch that took away her family
